---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — elloloop" description="elloloop privacy policy — how we collect, use, and protect your data.">
  <div class="prose">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <h2>1. Collection of Information</h2>
    <p>We collect the phone number provided during registration for secure login and communication purposes.</p>

    <h2>2. Contact Access</h2>
    <p>elloloop requires access to your contacts to enable task delegation and reminder scheduling. We do not store or share contact information without explicit user consent.</p>

    <h2>3. Task and Reminder Data</h2>
    <p>Information related to tasks and reminders is stored securely on our servers. This data is used solely for the purpose of providing task management and reminder services.</p>

    <h2>4. Security Measures</h2>
    <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect user data, including encryption and secure protocols.</p>

    <h2>5. User Control</h2>
    <p>Users have the option to modify or delete their task and reminder data. Additionally, users can control access to their contacts within the app settings.</p>

    <h2>6. Communication</h2>
    <p>elloloop may use the provided email address for important communications, such as account recovery or service-related updates.</p>

    <h2>7. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>elloloop may use third-party services for analytics and improvement purposes. These services adhere to their own privacy policies.</p>

    <h2>8. Updates to Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>Our privacy policy may be updated to reflect changes in data handling practices. Users will be notified of any significant changes.</p>

    <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      By using elloloop, you agree to the terms outlined in this privacy policy.
      If you have any questions or concerns, please contact us at
      <a href="mailto:info@elloloop.com">info@elloloop.com</a>.
      We strive to respond to all inquiries in a timely manner.
    </p>

    <h2>10. Additional Contact Information</h2>
    <p>
      <strong>elloloop ltd.</strong><br />
      Address: 14 Featherstone Road, London, England, NW7 2BN<br />
      Phone: +44 776642428<br />
      Email: <a href="mailto:info@elloloop.com">info@elloloop.com</a>
    </p>
    <p>
      We value your privacy and are committed to addressing any inquiries
      or concerns you may have regarding the handling of your personal information.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
